He also lost his parents and his brother if I am not mistaken. But most importantly, Marty Mar might have been dealing with some substance abuse issues back in his hey day. Almost dying is enough to humble a SMART man. Martin is wealthy, world renowned and has the love of his family and friends. Dude is just chillin now. That wild, wired up Martin that we came to know and love may be behind him. He has grown and is a middle aged man now.
